BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 658 Td (Sarah had not taken a bath alone in three years. Every time she tried, guilt) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (crept in: she should be reading to the kids, cleaning, or being productive. Then) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (one day she collapsed from exhaustion at the grocery store. Her doctor said:) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td ('You cannot pour from an empty cup.' That day changed everything.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 583 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 578 m 155 578 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 560 Td (Mom guilt is a cultural myth that tells you that being a good mother means) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 546 Td (completely erasing yourself. This is not only untrue, it is harmful to you AND) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 532 Td (your children.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 510 Td (Children learn self-care by watching their mothers practice it. When you take) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 496 Td (care of yourself, you are teaching your kids that their needs matter too. You) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 482 Td (are modeling healthy boundaries.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 460 Td (The lie of mom guilt says: good mothers sacrifice everything. The truth says:) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 446 Td (good mothers know that their wellbeing directly impacts their children's) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 432 Td (wellbeing. A depleted mom cannot show up fully.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 410 Td (Permission slip: You are allowed to rest. You are allowed to have hobbies. You) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 396 Td (are allowed to say 'not right now.' You are allowed to close the bathroom door.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 382 Td (You are a person, not just a role.) Tj ET

endstream
