BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (body ached. Her back hurt from carrying babies. Her energy was at zero. She) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (thought physical self-care meant going to the gym, which felt impossible. Then) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (she learned that physical self-care starts much simpler.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 583 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 578 m 155 578 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 560 Td (Physical self-care when exhausted is about the basics: sleep, hydration,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 546 Td (nutrition, movement, and touch. When you are depleted, start at the foundation.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 524 Td (Sleep: If you cannot get more hours, improve quality. Black-out curtains, no) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 510 Td (phone 30 minutes before bed, cooler room temperature, and a consistent bedtime) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 496 Td (make a real difference.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 474 Td (Hydration: Most moms are chronically dehydrated. Keep a large water bottle in) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 460 Td (every room. Set a goal of finishing one by noon. Dehydration worsens fatigue,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 446 Td (headaches, and irritability.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 424 Td (Movement: Forget hour-long workouts. Walk around the block while kids are in the) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 410 Td (stroller. Do squats while waiting for the microwave. Stretch during naptime.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 396 Td (Even 10 minutes counts.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 374 Td (Touch: When was the last time someone touched you without needing something? Ask) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 360 Td (your partner for a 2-minute shoulder rub. Get a massage if possible. Physical) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 346 Td (touch reduces cortisol.) Tj ET

endstream
