BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 658 Td (Despite being exhausted beyond measure, Michelle lay awake at night with her) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 643 Td (mind racing. She worried about everything: was that cough serious, did she sign) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 628 Td (the permission slip, is her marriage okay, will her child be happy. The cruelest) Tj ET
BT 0.25 g /F4 11 Tf 72 613 Td (irony of motherhood: too tired to function but too wired to sleep.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F2 12 Tf 72 583 Td (THE LESSON) Tj ET
q 0.4 G 1 w 72 578 m 155 578 l S Q
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 560 Td (Insomnia in mothers is epidemic. Your nervous system is on high alert 24/7) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 546 Td (because you are responsible for keeping small humans alive. Even when your body) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 532 Td (can rest, your brain often will not.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 510 Td (Sleep hygiene for moms: same bedtime every night \(even when you could stay up\),) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 496 Td (no screens in bed \(the blue light plus scrolling keeps your brain active\), cool) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 482 Td (dark room, white noise to mask kid sounds that trigger your alert system.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 460 Td (Racing thoughts technique: keep a notepad by your bed. When a thought comes,) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 446 Td (write it down and tell your brain 'handled, I will deal with it tomorrow.' This) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 432 Td (externalizes the thought so your brain can let go.) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 410 Td (If you cannot sleep: do not fight it. Get up, do something boring in dim light) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 396 Td (\(fold laundry, read something dull\), and return to bed when drowsy. Lying in bed) Tj ET
BT 0.2 g /F1 10 Tf 72 382 Td (frustrated makes insomnia worse.) Tj ET

